- I heard this is the birthing place of the Church of the one true Goddess. I want to join. 
	???: More and more people flocking to join each day. The Goddess welcomes you all with open arms. As do we. 
	- She showed Herself to me one night. Told me to come here. 
		???: The Elders told us She would soon send a chosen one bearing Her Gift. Safe to assume you're the one they've been talking about.
